      <para id="id1167458216552">FOR DISCUSSION:</para>
      <list id="id1167449682175" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Is your paper delivered?</item>
        <item>Why do YOU read the paper?</item>
        <item>Why is it important to read the papers?</item>
        <item>What makes some papers better than others?</item>
        <item>Which papers do you prefer?</item>
        <item>Why is it better to read more than one newspaper?</item>
      </list>
      <table id="id1167449343547" summary="">
        <tgroup cols="2">
          <colspec colnum="1" colname="c1"/>
          <colspec colnum="2" colname="c2"/>
          <tbody>
